<font color="#FF0000">MY SUCCESS IN TRUST</font><br>
<tt>Sun Nov 16 11:06:30 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I trust those who have integrity.  People will always fail you or not meet your expectations.  Many times it is our fault because we have failed to communicate to them what we expect.<br><br>
Failure when associated with the best effort is a part of life that I have learned to deal with.  Failure is merely a result of risk.  Those who continue to reach for something better.  It is merely a step in learning.  When I see failure without introspection I learn to distrust.  A matter of character.<br><br>
If we do not become myopic in our views we can deal better with trust.<br><br>
We should trust
